summary:
MD. Dermatologist with clinical experience on cutaneous lymphoma and Phototherapy and extracorporeal photopheresis or light therapy. Master ( c) in research.  
My objective is combine the clinical practice of my profession and research, bringing new knowledge in the field of dermatology.
